<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 06:21:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港领导人解雇两名高级官员，旨在“做得更好”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-sacks-two-senior-officials-aim-do-better-2024-12-05/</link><description>香港特首李家超周四表示，他出人意料地更换了两名高级官员，他表示此举将最大限度地提高社会和经济效益，并帮助香港“赶上”其他旅游目的地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:49:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-leader-sacks-two-senior-officials-aim-do-better-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>11 月份亚洲股市连续第二个月出现大量资金流出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-see-heavy-outflows-second-straight-month-november-2024-12-05/</link><description>由于担心明年即将上任的唐纳德·特朗普政府可能对地区出口征收关税，亚洲股市 11 月连续第二个月面临外国投资者的抛售压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:37:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/asian-stocks-see-heavy-outflows-second-straight-month-november-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚表示，美国对金砖国家征收的任何关税都可能影响半导体供应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-says-any-us-tariffs-brics-nations-could-impact-semiconductor-supply-2024-12-05/</link><description>马来西亚周四表示，即将上任的特朗普政府对金砖国家试图创造新货币或使用美元替代品征收关税的任何尝试都可能导致全球半导体供应链中断。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:23:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/malaysia-says-any-us-tariffs-brics-nations-could-impact-semiconductor-supply-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，台湾总统与美国众议院议长约翰逊通话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-spoke-with-us-house-speaker-johnson-sources-say-2024-12-05/</link><description>两位知情人士周四告诉路透社，台湾总统赖清德在访问太平洋期间与美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊通了电话，这次谈话可能会进一步激怒北京。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 04:42:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-spoke-with-us-house-speaker-johnson-sources-say-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>比特币突破 10 万美元，降息押注提振股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-05/</link><description>比特币周四突破 10 万美元，因投资者押注美国会出现友好的监管转变，而亚洲股市则坚挺，此前华尔街指数因对美国降息的信心不断增强而创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 02:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统在关岛表示：我们不会屈服于极权主义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/visiting-guam-taiwan-president-calls-fellow-democracies-unite-against-2024-12-05/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周四在美国领土关岛表示，台湾不会屈服于极权主义，称台湾和美国为“兄弟”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/visiting-guam-taiwan-president-calls-fellow-democracies-unite-against-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：首尔暂时平静，美国霸主继续前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 21:48:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>高级官员称，“大量”美国人的元数据被中国黑客窃取</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/large-number-americans-metadata-stolen-by-chinese-hackers-senior-official-says-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，一名美国高级官员对记者表示，在一个名为“盐台风”的中国黑客组织开展的大规模网络间谍活动中，大量美国人的元数据被盗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 21:18:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/large-number-americans-metadata-stolen-by-chinese-hackers-senior-official-says-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>信中称，电话公司拒绝美国军方索取安全数据的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/phone-firms-denying-us-military-requests-security-data-letter-says-2024-12-04/</link><description>根据周三发布的一封信，电话公司拒绝了美国军方提供有关美国电信系统漏洞数据的请求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 19:40:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/phone-firms-denying-us-military-requests-security-data-letter-says-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>独家：布林肯希望给继任者卢比奥尽可能的“最强牌”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-wants-give-successor-rubio-strongest-hand-possible-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三表示，他的重点是确保马可·卢比奥在下个月接替他时能够在包括乌克兰在内的重大外交政策问题上取得进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-wants-give-successor-rubio-strongest-hand-possible-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>拜登访问安哥拉之际，中国对非洲贫困国家实行免税准入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-duty-free-access-poor-african-states-kicks-biden-tours-angola-2024-12-04/</link><description>一位中国高级外交官表示，就在美国总统乔·拜登访问安哥拉之际，中国对非洲最不发达国家的零关税准入本周开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-duty-free-access-poor-african-states-kicks-biden-tours-angola-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>据 The Information 报道，苹果在将百度人工智能模型适应中国方面面临障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apple-facing-hurdles-adapting-baidu-ai-models-china-information-reports-2024-12-04/</link><description>据 The Information 周三报道，苹果和百度正在努力为在中国销售的 iPhone 添加人工智能功能，但面临着可能损害这家科技巨头在中国手机销售的障碍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 15:15:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apple-facing-hurdles-adapting-baidu-ai-models-china-information-reports-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员在通报中国盐台风电信黑客事件后誓言采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-agencies-brief-senators-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-04/</link><description>美国政府机构周三为所有参议员举行了一次机密简报会，内容涉及中国所谓的“盐台风”深入美国电信公司并窃取美国通话数据的行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-agencies-brief-senators-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>川崎重挫山东队亚冠，蔚山幸存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kawasaki-hand-shandong-asian-champions-league-thrashing-while-ulsan-stay-alive-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，川崎前锋以4-0大胜山东泰山队，增强了晋级亚冠精英赛淘汰赛的希望，而蔚山高清队则在下半场发起反击，击败了上海申花队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kawasaki-hand-shandong-asian-champions-league-thrashing-while-ulsan-stay-alive-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康任命高管接任被拘留的中国区负责人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-names-new-international-executive-vp-succeed-leon-wang-2024-12-04/</link><description>阿斯利康周三任命 Iskra Reic 为新任国际执行副总裁 (EVP)，接替 10 月份被中国当局拘留的 Leon Wang。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-names-new-international-executive-vp-succeed-leon-wang-2024-12-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>